---
---
<section class="section faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center animate-fadeUp">
      <div class="section-tag">FAQ</div>
      <h2 class="heading-lg">Answers to Your <span class="text-gradient-gold">Moving Questions</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-grid animate-fadeUp" id="faqGrid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span class="faq-question-text">How much do packers and movers cost in South India?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Local moves start from ₹3,999 and intercity relocations begin at ₹7,999. The final price depends on distance, volume of goods, services selected, and floor access. We always provide a fixed, transparent quote after a free survey — no hidden fees ever.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span class="faq-question-text">Is PackersHub IBA approved and government verified?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes! PackersHub is a fully IBA-approved moving company and is government-registered. All our staff are police-verified and we carry all required licenses and permits to operate across South India.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span class="faq-question-text">Do you provide insurance for goods during transit?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Absolutely. All our moves come with transit insurance. Our Starter plan includes ₹2 lakh coverage, Standard includes ₹5 lakh, and Premium offers up to ₹20 lakh coverage. Additional insurance can be purchased for high-value items.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span class="faq-question-text">How far in advance should I book my move?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>We recommend booking at least 7-10 days in advance for intercity moves and 3-5 days for local moves. However, we also offer emergency 24-hour moving services for urgent relocations — just call us!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span class="faq-question-text">Can you transport my car along with household goods?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes! We have specialized enclosed car carriers for safe vehicle transport. You can book car transport separately or bundle it with your household move for a discounted combined rate. GPS tracking is included.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">
          <span class="faq-question-text">What happens if my goods are damaged during the move?</span>
          <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>PackersHub offers a 100% Damage-Free Guarantee. If any item is damaged due to our handling, we replace or compensate for it — no questions asked. File a claim within 48 hours of delivery and we resolve within 7 business days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq { background: var(--white); padding: 100px 0; }
  .faq-grid { max-width: 900px; margin: 60px auto 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .faq-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .faq-item.open { border-color: var(--blue-300); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); }
  .faq-question {
    padding: 24px 32px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    background: var(--white);
    transition: 0.3s;
  }
  .faq-question:hover { background: var(--gray-50); }
  .faq-question-text { font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .faq-toggle {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    background: var(--gray-100);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--gray-600);
    transition: 0.4s;
  }
  .faq-item.open .faq-toggle { transform: rotate(45deg); background: var(--blue-600); color: var(--white); }
  
  .faq-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.5s cubic-bezier(0, 1, 0, 1);
    background: var(--white);
  }
  .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 1000px; transition: max-height 1s ease-in; }
  .faq-answer p { padding: 0 32px 32px; font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.7; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(q => {
    q.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const item = q.parentElement;
      const isOpen = item?.classList.contains('open');
      
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));
      
      if (!isOpen) {
        item?.classList.add('open');
      }
    });
  });
</script>
